Modal Soul is Nujabes' followup album to 2003's Metaphorical Music. Like its predecessor, it maintains a combination of hip hop and jazz. Features artists Cise Starr, Akin, Terry Callier, Shing02, Substantial, Pase Rock, Apani B and Uyama Hiroto
